a025480(int) - Static method in class net.jnellis.interleave.Util
Corresponds to an integer sequence of the https://oeis.org/A025480 which generates the index positions for the proper sequence of swaps (and swap backs) for the interleave operation, given that series of swaps was done sequentially and in order.
